Ensure that there is sufficient space in the target inventory before attempting to insert items. Regularly monitor and manage inventory levels to prevent overflow.

### NAMESPACE

#### Important Variables
- `iron_ore_inventory`: Dict[str, int] - Tracks the inventory of iron ore in various chests.
